{"id":148278,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/柬泰边境冲突继续/","date":"2011-04-28T08:00:20Z","modified":"2011-04-28T08:00:20Z","title":"柬泰边境冲突继续","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">曼谷</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">泰国和柬埔寨之间的边境武装冲突周四（4月2</span><span>8</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日）进入第7天，死亡人数升至15人。据法新社一名记者报道，在距两国共同边界线约20公里的帕侬地区（Phanom Dongrak）可听见爆炸声。一名柬军上校称，交战目前再度集中于帕威夏神庙所在地区的两座寺庙附近。两国均称对相关地区拥有主权。连日来的边境冲突已导致两国数以万计的居民背井离乡。2008年以来，当地一再发生边境冲突。当年，柬埔寨在与泰国关于帕威夏神庙的主权争议中获胜，得到联合国认可，将该神庙列入世界文化遗产名录。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com\"><img src=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com/images/1x1.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"ftrf - full text rss\" /></a><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15034191%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E6%9F%AC%E6%B3%B0%E8%BE%B9%E5%A2%83%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}